---
title: Pork & Roasted Veggie Fettuccine with Parmesan & Basil
description: In this dish, we've teamed the traditional Italian tomato sauce with seasoned pork mince and roasted veggies for a meal that looks every bit as good as it tastes. First dibs gets an extra sprinkling of Parmesan!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tuscan-pork-roasted-veggie-spaghetti-bf3ad0e9.jpg
